  "title": "Retired members in a British union",
  "abstract": "This research note examines pensioner activism in a major British union, the Public and Commercial Services Union (PCS). The subject is an important one for unions’ future development: if they can become effective vehicles for pensioner activism, they may widen their social appeal beyond the employed.",
